data.description: Welcome to 1663 Barrywood Circle E, this split-level home offers so many amazing features! The upstairs living and dining room boast hardwood floors and the kitchen is flooded with natural light. The upper floor has 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms including the primary bedroom with triple trey ceilings, plush carpets, and an en-suite bathroom. The lower level features a cozy living space with a beautiful built-in entertainment console, 1 bedroom, and 1 full bathroom. The full laundry room is conveniently located on the lower level, as well as the entry to the home’s 2-car garage. The backyard is a dream. Enjoy the back deck, stone fire pit, and space for pets, kids, or entertaining with an oversized driveway! Find your home sweet home in quiet Clarksville, TN.  Seller is offering a 1 year home warranty for $575 from ACHOSA and $5,000 towards Buyer's closing cost or rate buy down!
